headline: UBS Maintains Buy on Arch Capital Group, Raises Price Target to $114
summary: UBS  analyst Brian Meredith   maintains Arch Capital Group (NASDAQ:ACGL) with a Buy and raises the price target from $113 to $114.

headline: Cantor Fitzgerald Maintains Neutral on Arch Capital Group, Raises Price Target to $100
summary: Cantor Fitzgerald  analyst Ryan Tunis   maintains Arch Capital Group (NASDAQ:ACGL) with a Neutral and raises the price target from $97 to $100.
